title: Nice features, very good, but too small buffer
comment: I was looking for an Android app to monitor my wireless arduinos (panstamps) activities. I tried a few, and this one is the best of the pack : the ability to send the buffer by email is very nice, and its ability to start automatically when connecting the USB device is very good as well.  The only annoying fact is that the buffer is limited to about 5kBytes, and there is no way to increase it. This means I frequently interesting data. I wish I could extend it at least tenfold. (what's a 64kB email nowadays ?)
